		Answer:
answer:
The answer is: **Parliament of Nepal, House of Representatives (Nepal), Federal Parliament of Nepal, National Assembly (Nepal)**

Technically, there are various official and unofficial names for the Nepalese parliament. Of the options provided in the question, the most accurate answer is **Parliament of Nepal, House of Representatives (Nepal), and Federal Parliament of Nepal**.

The permanent official name is "Parliament of Nepal". It is also sometimes informally called "Parliament of Nepal" or "Federal Parliament of Nepal".
